  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast can be chosen off the menu the day before. You'll have a choice of croissants, cakes, bread, pancakes and savoury options including eggs, bacon, cold meats and cheese. You can even choose where you'd like to have your breakfast. The breakfast room has lovely views across Lake Garda and the Sirmione peninsula. When the weather's warm you can even have your breakfast in the garden.</p>
<p>Afternoon tea with biscuits is available free of charge for all Inghams guests, every day between 3pm and 5pm. Please request your tea before hand.</p>
<p>During the day the poolside bar serves drinks, snacks and light dishes like salads and pasta. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
