  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Garden View Rooms</strong> sleep two people and have a balcony. The rooms are comfortable and well maintained, with a bit of a retro feel. Facilities include air conditioning, fridge, TV, a bath with overhead shower and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Lake View Rooms </strong>sleep up to two people. They have great views across Lake Garda from their private balconies. These rooms have a shower. </p>
<p><strong>Sole Occupancy Rooms </strong>are also available with a balcony and mountain or lake views. These rooms all have a bath with an overhead shower. They're available on request, so please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
